videos.headline: ODU's Smartt races for the end zone
videos.description: Stone Smartt keeps it on the option and runs in a 10-yard touchdown to increase Old Dominion's lead on Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (ODU's Smartt races for the end zone) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Geiger sheds would-be tacklers for 47-yard ODU TD
videos.description: Stone Smartt hits a wide-open Matt Geiger, who breaks a couple of tackles for a 47-yard Old Dominion touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Geiger sheds would-be tacklers for 47-yard ODU TD) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Taulapapa muscles into the end zone to give UVa its first lead
videos.description: Wayne Taulapapa takes the handoff and goes up the gut for a seven-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taulapapa muscles into the end zone to give UVa its first lead) 2019/09/21
